        <p>Mutation analysis was done at the Department of Research and Development, Faculty of Medicine, Siriraj Hospital Mahidol University, Bangkok. Mutation screening in 14 exons of <italic>PAX6</italic> was performed using single strand conformation polymorphism (SSCP) followed by direct DNA sequencing. The primers used are as mentioned by Atchaneeyasakul et al. [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="r7">7</xref>] and shown in <xref ref-type="table" rid="t1">Table 1</xref>.</p>
